nodes.bodyText:
Ah, sorry - yes, you are correct. It should declare artifacts, the configuration to attach them to and the outputs. An example is in solr/example/build.gradle:
artifacts {
  packaging packagingDir, {
    builtBy assemblePackaging
  }
}
